{"tid":1260083,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4] 《新櫻花大戰》公開了19分鐘實機試玩影像 預定於冬季登陸PS4平台","createTime":"2019-06-26T17:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T11:53:09.000Z","uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a4b1c36b80a9a8a1b7f64274e171486061f65185","tid":1260083,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:59:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P78vYtU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP78vYtU.jpg&h=f9858e81&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D05m48V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD05m48V.jpg&h=7aa001ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《新櫻花大戰》在今日的直播節目上公開了約19分鐘的大劇場探索實機試玩影像，玩家可以操控主角自由行動，在地上還能撿到各種舊角色的照片，其他主要是日常冒險和交流部分。<br />\n<br />\n《新櫻花大戰》目前預定於今冬登陸PS4平台，並已經確定會推出繁體中文版。在直播中幾位表示下次的節目預定在7月播出，而他們也不小心透露本作中將有上海華擊團的存在，預定在今後向大家介紹。<br />\n<br />\n19分鐘實機試玩影像:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Nmia.Gaming/videos/621662045021223/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNmia.Gaming%2Fvideos%2F621662045021223%2F&d=7GYMv7TAV12u%2FDK%2BXNcYJZS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=807a36d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Nmia.Gaming/videos/621662045021223/</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀:<br />\n[新．櫻花大戰．卍解] 【FAMI通《新．櫻花大戰》開發成員采訪要點】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1141560/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1141560/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ec865b96cf8058cd9320a1fd43568007c3faf092","tid":1260083,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T21:08:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a2e9d272fb4e8de315b3004cdca4e569613070b","tid":1260083,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T23:33:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3606aee33517a1a7f172bea8b46a7a85f3d08f5","tid":1260083,"uid":1238